# --- UPLOADS ---

### Upload Single File
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-assets/test.jpg
--boundary--

### Upload Documents (Signup)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/upload-documents
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="uploadId"; filename="id.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-assets/id.jpg
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="proofOfOwnership"; filename="ownership.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-assets/ownership.jpg
--boundary--


